<view class="container">
  <view class="status-card {{state.loggedIn && state.hasKey ? 'on' : ''}}">
    <view class="status-dot"></view>
    <view class="status-body">
      <view class="status-title">{{state.loggedIn && state.hasKey ? '云同步已开启' : '云同步未开启'}}</view>
      <view class="status-sub muted">
        <block wx:if="{{!state.loggedIn}}">请先登录同一个账号</block>
        <block wx:elif="{{!state.hasKey}}">生成新主密钥，或使用 APP 备份的助记词恢复</block>
        <block wx:else>主密钥保存在本地，服务端无法读取明文</block>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="guide-card">
    <view class="guide-title">云同步功能使用方法</view>
    <view class="guide-line">1. 已在 APP 上传过数据：小程序必须恢复 APP 备份的同一组助记词。</view>
    <view class="guide-line">2. 首次在小程序开通：生成主密钥，离线备份 24 个助记词，再立即推送。</view>
    <view class="guide-line">3. 更换设备或重装后：登录同一个账号，恢复同一组助记词，再拉取云端。</view>
    <view class="guide-line">4. 新生成的主密钥不能解密旧主密钥上传的数据。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card" wx:if="{{state.loggedIn}}">
    <view class="card-title">生成主密钥</view>
    <view class="card-sub muted">首次开通云同步时使用</view>
    <view class="body-text">系统会在本地生成 32 字节 UMK，并写入小程序本地存储。服务端始终只看到密文。</view>
    <button class="btn-solid single-btn" bindtap="onGenerateMasterKey" disabled="{{busy}}">
      {{busy ? '处理中...' : '生成主密钥'}}
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="card" wx:if="{{state.loggedIn}}">
    <view class="card-title">助记词备份</view>
    <view class="card-sub muted">请离线抄写，丢失后无法恢复云端密文</view>

    <view wx:if="{{generatedMnemonic}}" class="mnemonic-box">
      <view class="mnemonic-word" wx:for="{{generatedWords}}" wx:key="*this">
        {{index + 1}}. {{item}}
      </view>
    </view>
    <view wx:else class="empty-box">生成主密钥后，助记词会显示在这里。</view>

    <view class="btn-row" wx:if="{{generatedMnemonic}}">
      <button class="btn-ghost" bindtap="onCopyGeneratedMnemonic">复制助记词</button>
    </view>
    <checkbox-group bindchange="onBackupConfirmChange" wx:if="{{generatedMnemonic}}">
      <label class="check-row">
        <checkbox value="confirmed" checked="{{backupConfirmed}}" />
        <text>我已离线备份助记词</text>
      </label>
    </checkbox-group>
  </view>

  <view class="card" wx:if="{{state.loggedIn}}">
    <view class="card-title">恢复主密钥</view>
    <view class="card-sub muted">更换设备、重装，或同步 APP 云端数据时使用</view>
    <textarea
      class="textarea"
      placeholder="输入 APP 或小程序备份的 24 个助记词"
      maxlength="-1"
      auto-height="true"
      value="{{mnemonic}}"
      bindinput="onMnemonicInput"
    />
    <button class="btn-ghost single-btn" bindtap="onRestoreMnemonic" disabled="{{busy}}">
      恢复到本地
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="card" wx:if="{{state.loggedIn && state.hasKey}}">
    <view class="card-title">同步操作</view>
    <view class="kv-row">
      <text>本地可推送</text>
      <text class="strong">{{state.queueLen}} 条</text>
    </view>
    <view class="kv-row">
      <text>上次推送</text>
      <text class="muted">{{lastPushLabel}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="kv-row">
      <text>设备 ID</text>
      <text class="muted ellipsis">{{state.deviceId}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="kv-row">
      <text>密钥指纹</text>
      <text class="muted ellipsis">{{state.keyFingerprint}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn-solid" bindtap="onPush" disabled="{{busy}}">
        {{busy ? '处理中...' : '立即推送'}}
      </button>
      <button class="btn-ghost" bindtap="onPull" disabled="{{busy}}">
        {{busy ? '处理中...' : '拉取云端'}}
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tip" wx:if="{{state.loggedIn && state.hasKey}}" bindtap="onGoMembership">
    推送 / 拉取需要账号拥有 cloud_sync 权益。点击进入会员中心。
  </view>

  <view class="tip muted">
    如果你想同步 APP 已上传的数据，请不要在小程序重新生成主密钥，必须粘贴 APP 原来备份的助记词。
  </view>

  <view class="log-card" wx:if="{{logs.length}}">
    <view class="card-title">操作日志</view>
    <view class="log-line" wx:for="{{logs}}" wx:key="t">
      <text class="log-t muted">{{item.t}}</text>
      <text class="log-msg">{{item.msg}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
